trans-unit.source: Create or Update a BizTalk Service
trans-unit.target: Create or Update a BizTalk Service

trans-unit.source: This topic provides information on how to create/update new <token>af_integration</token> in a specified subscription and cloud service.
trans-unit.target: This topic provides information on how to create/update new <token>af_integration</token> in a specified subscription and cloud service.

trans-unit.source: This section provides information about the request operation to create or update a <token>af_integration</token> deployment.
trans-unit.target: This section provides information about the request operation to create or update a <token>af_integration</token> deployment.

trans-unit.source: <legacyItalic>cloud-service-name</legacyItalic> is the unique name for the cloud service that hosts your BizTalk Service.
trans-unit.target: <legacyItalic>cloud-service-name</legacyItalic> is the unique name for the cloud service that hosts your BizTalk Service.

trans-unit.source: The name can be up to 64 characters in length.
trans-unit.target: The name can be up to 64 characters in length.

trans-unit.source: The name must be unique and must range between 6 and 20 characters in length.
trans-unit.target: The name must be unique and must range between 6 and 20 characters in length.
